people in through building capacity and empowering community, local government 
and duty bearer to develop context specific technology, approach and adaptive 
planning in an integrated manner with multi-sectoral coordination. &nbsp; Major activities that 
will be implemented are: 
</font><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Conducting study to asses and 
long term prediction of climate change impact on WASH sector in the project 
area; Exploring and introducing 
suitable and scalable climate adaptive WASH technology to ensure greater access 
