yle="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;"> </span></span><span style="color: black;">Construction of 6 school handwashing facilities with five taps each</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr style="height: 23.25pt;"> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; height: 23.25pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860" valign="top"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;"><b><span>Outcome/Result 2</span></b><b><span>:</span></b><b><span style="color: black;"> To provide 7,000</span></b><b><span style="color: red;"> </span></b><b><span style="color: black;">people with access to improved sanitation</span></b></p> </td> </tr> <tr style="height: 17.95pt;"> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; height: 17.95pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860" valign="top"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><b><span>Activity 2:</span></b></p> </td> </tr> <tr style="height: 19.75pt;"> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; height: 19.75pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="color: black;">2.1. Construction of 6 school sanitary blocs</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="color: black;">2.2. Construction / Rehabilitation of 7 sanitary blocs for the health center</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span>2.3. Construction of 7 incinerators for health center</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="color: black;">2.4. Training local masons to construct slabs and encourage households to construct their own latrines through CLTS</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860" valign="top"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><b><span>Outcome/Result 3</span></b><b><span style="color: black;">: To provide </span></b><b><span>4,000<span style="color: red;"> </span><span style="color: black;">people with hygiene education and capacity building</span></span></b></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860" valign="top"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><b><span>Activity 3:</span></b></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="color: black;">3.1. Community based hygiene promotion meetings (VAD, FOCUS GROUP, Etc.)</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="color: black;">3.2. Hygiene promotion celebration (World Water Day, World Toilet Day &amp; Global Handwashing Day)</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span>3.3. Wash Friendly Institution Training (School, Health center)</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr style="height: 33.55pt;"> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; height: 33.55pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span>3.4. Advocacy and Capacity building of local structures: stratégie de promotion de l'hygiène, santé maternelle, santé neo-natale, MHM, HRBA, CLTS, sanitation marketing.</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr style="height: 33.55pt;"> <td style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 515.7pt; height: 33.55pt; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;" width="860"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span>3.5.</span><span style="color: black; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; font-size: 8pt;"> </span><span style="color: black;">Survey, monitoring and evaluation.</span></p> </td> </tr> </tbody></table> <p style="margin: 1em 0px;"><b><span>&nbsp;Estimated cost - £288,530 (Ar1,298,384,500 in local currency) - Fully Unfunded</span></b></p> <p style="margin: 1em 0px;"><span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;<strong>Estimated timeframe</strong> - 12 months</p> <h1 style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span><font size="5" color="#5b9bd5" face="Arial">3. Where?</font></span></h1> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;">&nbsp;<span style="color: black; font-size: 11pt;">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 11pt;">This project will ensure the following interventions and expected results:</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;">-<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">Water connection and construction of sanitary blocks equipped with a shower and incinerators at:</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 78.55pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Wingdings;">§<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">Two District-Level Reference Hospital Centres (Anjepy and Manjakandriana)</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 78.55pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Wingdings;">§<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">Four Level 2 Basic Health Centres: Anjepy, Ambanitsena, Ambohitrolomahitsy and Ankazondany</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 78.55pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Wingdings;">§<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">One Level 1 Basic Health Centre: Anjohy (Ankazondandy)</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;">-<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">Rehabilitation of one water supply system (in Anjepy)</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: black; font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;">-<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">100% of health care staffs in the district trained on key thematic like WASH fit approach, emergency obstetric and neonatal care, maternal, newborn and child health, integrated management of childhood illness at health centre and community level, hygiene promotion.</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;">-<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">Setting up of a sustainability system for the facilities in place.</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Calibri,sans-serif;">-<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">Healthy start campaign at national and local level.</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Calibri,sans-serif; font-size: 14pt;">-<span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="color: black;">Health attendance rates and particularly birth attended by qualified personnel increased by 20% in at least 7 health care facilities. </span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span>&nbsp;</span></p> <h1 style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span><font size="5" color="#5b9bd5" face="Arial">4. Who?</font></span></h1> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>  <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span>The use of the fund will be divided into two parts, some of which will be managed directly by WaterAid Madagascar, in particular for local and national hygiene promotion activities, policy and advocacy. On the other hand, one part will be managed by the WaterAid partner for the direct construction activities of the WASH infrastructures and the actions of awareness and education in hygiene with the communities. We will also work with local partners such as companies providing services for the construction of WASH works, NGOs or local associations for the conduct of SOFT activities and institutional support in the field. And we will collaborate with the Regional Directorate of Public Health Analamanga, the Regional Directorate of the EAH Analamanga, the School Health Division of the Ministry of National Education and the Ministry of Public Health in charge of maternal, neonatal and infant and WASH activities in the promotion of hygiene and sanitation.</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;"><span>Finally, we will collaborate with the population of the Municipality of </span><span>Manjakandriana</span><span> adopts sustainable integrated hygiene behaviours as social norms.</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span>We will also promote innovation and research of new technologies adapted to urban areas in order to strengthen the production capacity of Jirama and meet the populations' drinking water, sanitation and hygiene needs in urban areas. We will work with the national company Jirama for connecting the facilities that we will build in urban areas to the drinking water network</span></p></p></div><button class="accordion">Madagascar | 2- SUSTAINABLE PROGRAMME DELIVERY | RANO WASH Project- CSD | OdileRandriamananjara@wateraid.org | target funding: GBP <strong>1,168,916</strong><br></button> <div class="panel"><p><h1 style="text-align: left;" align="left"><strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="windowtext" face="Arial,sans-serif">Project Statement</font></strong></h1> <h1 style="text-align: left;" align="left"><strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" color="windowtext" face="Arial,sans-serif">WaterAid [Country name]</font></strong></h1>  <table style="width: 100%;" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"> <tbody><tr> <td style="background: rgb(242, 242, 242); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; border: 1pt solid rgb(127, 127, 127); width: 24.72%; text-align: left;" width="24%" valign="top"> <p style="margin-bottom: 0pt;"><strong><font style="font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial,sans-serif">Name of programme</font></strong></p> </td> <td style="border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 75.28%; text-align: left; border-top-color: rgb(127, 127, 127); border-right-color: rgb(127, 127, 127); border-bottom-color: rgb(127, 127, 127);" colspan="3" width="75%" valign="top"> <p style="margin-bottom: 0pt;"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;" lang="EN-GB">Sustainable Programme Delivery</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style="background: rgb(242, 242, 242); border-width: medium 1pt 1pt; border-style: non