tyle="font-size: 12pt;">1. Why?</font></h2> <p style="margin-bottom: 0pt;"><font color="black" face="Arial,sans-serif" style="font-size: 12pt;"></font><strong><font color="#ffb612" face="Arial,sans-serif" style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</font></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12pt;">Sustainability of WASH infrastructure and services still remains a 
  challenge at both national and district level. For instance, over 25% of community 
