review of guidelines for community management of RPWSS</span></i></font></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; text-align: justify;"><span><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p> <p style="margin: 1em 0px; text-align: justify;"><b><span>Estimated cost</span></b></p> <p style="margin: 1em 0px; text-align: justify;"><span>Estimated project budget in GBP is 2,000,000. The project will run for a period of 36 months but so far, funds have not been secured for the project. </span></p> <p style="margin: 1em 0px; text-align: justify;"><b><span>In terms of sustainability, the project will</span></b></p> <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0cm;"> <li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; font-weight: normal;"><i><span>Improve the capacity of community management structures to ensure that the service continue to even beyond the system’s installation</span></i></li> </ul> <ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; font-weight: normal;"><p style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><i><span>Improve the policy environment for hygiene whose actions will remain beyond the project period. </span></i></p></li></ul> <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0cm;"> <li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; font-weight: normal;"><i><span>Work with district local government and line ministries to ensure that the proposed changes and actions are effected within the local governance system and are therefore sustainable </span></i></li> </ul> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><i><span><font face="Arial">New innovations in the project will include;</font></span></i></p> <ul type="disc" style="margin-top: 0cm;"> <li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; font-weight: normal;"><i><span>Hygiene behaviour change model of ABCDE Methodology</span></i></li> </ul> <ul style="list-style-type: disc;"><li style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; font-weight: normal;"><p style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0cm; margin-bottom: 0pt;"><i><span>Increasing yield using solar powered boreholes and battery storage</span></i></p></li></ul> <p style="margin: 1em 0px; text-align: justify;"><b><span>&nbsp;</span></b></p> <h1 style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 37.8pt; text-align: justify;"><font color="#009fda"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial">2.</font><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial">Where?</font></span></font></h1> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;"><span><font face="Arial">The project will be implemented in the 2 districts of Machinga and Nkhotakota and it will target 20,000 marginalised people with access to safe water and 40,000 people with improved sanitation.</font></span></p> <h1 style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 37.8pt; text-align: justify;"><font color="#009fda"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial">3.</font><span style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 7pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial">Who?</font></span></font></h1> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt; text-align: justify;"><span><font face="Arial">The project will be implemented by existing local NGO partners who will be operating in the district at that time. the Local NGO partner will work closely with the District Council and community structures. </font></span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p></p></div><button class="accordion">Malawi | Sustainable Programme Delivery (SPD) | Malawi wathu wathanzi | anniemsosa@wateraid.org | target funding: GBP700,000<br></button> <div class="panel"><p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><b><span style="font-size: 14px;">Project Statement </span></b></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">WaterAid Malawi</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 8pt;"><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p> <table width="100%" style="border: currentColor; border-image: none; width: 100%;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"> <tbody><tr> <td width="25%" valign="top" style="background: rgb(242, 242, 242); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; border: 1pt solid rgb(127, 127, 127); border-image: none; width: 25.52%; text-align: left;"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><b><span><font face="Arial">Name of programme</font></span></b></p> </td> <td width="74%" valign="top" style="border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 74.48%; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;" colspan="3"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span><font face="Arial">Sustainable Program Delivery</font></span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width="25%" valign="top" style="background: rgb(242, 242, 242); border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 25.52%; text-align: left;"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><b><span><font face="Arial">Name of project</font></span></b></p> </td> <td width="74%" valign="top" style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 74.48%; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;" colspan="3"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span><font face="Arial">Malawi Wathu wa Thanzi</font></span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width="25%" valign="top" style="background: rgb(242, 242, 242); border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 25.52%; text-align: left;"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><b><span><font face="Arial">Prepared by</font></span></b></p></td><td width="28%" valign="top" style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 28.66%; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;"> Takondwa Kaliwo</td> <td width="29%" valign="top" style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 29.2%; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;">  </td> <td width="16%" valign="top" style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 16.62%; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span><font face="Arial">15/05/2017</font></span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width="25%" valign="top" style="background: rgb(242, 242, 242); border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 25.52%; text-align: left;"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><b><span><font face="Arial">Approved by</font></span></b></p> </td> <td width="28%" valign="top" style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 28.66%; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><font face="Arial">Annie Msosa</font></p> </td> <td width="29%" valign="top" style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 29.2%; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span><font face="Arial">Programme Manager</font></span></p> </td> <td width="16%" valign="top" style="border-width: 0px 1pt 1pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 16.62%; text-align: left; background-color: transparent;"> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span><font face="Arial">16/05/2017</font></span></p> </td> </tr> </tbody></table> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 11pt;"><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><font face="Arial">&nbsp;</font></span></p> <h1 style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">1. Why?</span></h1> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">Malawi continues to lose much needed financial and human resources every year because more than half of the population (59%) do not have access to improved sanitation (toilets) and an even higher proportion (63%) practice poor hygiene practices. Currently, more than half of the health sector budget (52%), which takes the second largest proportion of the national budget after the ministry of education, is spent on treating diseases that could have been avoided if only the population had adequate sanitation and improved hygiene practices. Sanitation and hygiene service are not only poor in people’s home but also in many health care facilities which do not have access to sufficient amounts of water, toilets and other necessary facilities to allow them to maintain a clean environment that can protect patients and guardians from infections. As a result of this patients who visit the hospital, especially women who come to deliver their babies and the babies themselves are at risk of contracting infections in the very place that is supposed to treat them. Children, especially those under the age of five (38%), often suffer from recurrent diarrhoea which affects their ability to absorb nutrients from food thereby negatively affecting their growth and development. Despite this situation financial investment in sanitation and hygiene remains very low across all the relevant sectors of health, education, nutrition, water and the environment. This is also the case at household level where people’s willingness to invest in good sanitation and hygiene facilities is low. At the ministerial level, leadership for sanitation and hygiene remains unresolved making operationalisation of sanitation prioritisation a challenge even though it is already prioritised within the country’s development strategy. At the policy level the Sanitation Policy which was developed in 2006 is outdated and the sanitation bill which is supposed&nbsp; to regulate sanitation and hygiene services in the country remains in draft form. Al these factors are contributing towards slow improvements in sanitation and hygiene.&nbsp; </span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">Key issues&nbsp; this project will aim to address.</span></p> <ul><li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">Weak leadership and political will for improved sanitation and hygiene</span></li><li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">Poor financing for sanitation and hygiene </span></li><li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">Weak policy environment and unclear institutional arrangement for sanitation and hygiene</span></li></ul>   <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">&nbsp;</span></p> <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12px;">WaterAid has been implementing sanitation and hygiene programs targeting households, schools and health centers&nbsp;levels targeting&nbsp;in small geographical units as entry points across 11 districts. WaterAid has also been a key player in the formulation and championing of the national Open Defecation Free (ODF) strategy by supporting its targeted communities to attain stop open defecation. Key lessons from these have been the needs to consolidate efforts at target whole districts for open defecation free status. WaterAid’s new country strategy deliberately committed to increasing focus on sanitation and hygiene a on sanitation and hygiene as a public health issues by promoting its prioritization at all levels.</span></font></p><p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12px;">&nbsp;</span></font></p> <h1 style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">2. What?</span></h1> <ul><li style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;"><b><span>Project theme</span></b> – Improved access to sanitation and hygiene at household, institutional level and in other public places</span></p></li><li style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;"><b><span>Estimated cost</span></b> – GBP700,000</span></p></li><li style="text-align: justify;"><p style="margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;"><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><span>Estimated&nbsp;</span></b><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><b>time frame</b>&nbsp;– 3 years</span></font></p></li><li style="text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal;"><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;"><b><span>Existing WaterAid experience</span></b> – more than 2 years’ experience</span></p></li><li style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12px;">3. Where?</span></li></ul>   <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><font face="Arial"><span style="font-size: 12px;">The project will be implemented at national level with some district level interventions&nbsp;in the following districts: Machinga, Nkhotakota, Kasungu, Dowa and Lilongwe</span></font></p> <h1 style="margin: 0cm 